message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm pleased with the service I've received so far but I have a question about my policy.
That's great to hear! I'd be more than happy to help you with your query. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Of course, my full name is Sarah Johnson.
Thank you for confirming, Sarah. Can you also provide me with your date of birth?
Great, thank you, Sarah. Finally, could you confirm the first line of your address and postcode?
Thank you for completing security. How can I assist you with your policy concern today?
I've recently had a car accident, and I'm unsure if my policy covers the repairs. Can you help me with that?
I'm sorry to hear about your accident, Sarah. Let me check your policy details to see if repairs are covered. Please allow me a moment to look into this for you.
Thank you for checking, Chris. I appreciate your assistance.

I've reviewed your policy, Sarah. It looks like the repairs are covered under your current plan. A possible resolution could be to file a claim and get the repair process started. Does this work for you?
That's all sorted, Chris. Filing a claim would be great. Thank you for your help!
I'm glad we could help you with this, Sarah. If you need any further assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
Thank you, Chris. You've been very helpful. Have a great day too!
